{"title":"麦场随想曲","authors":["赵启顺"],"dates":[{"year":1996,"month":6,"day":21}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"麦场随想曲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赵启顺"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打麦机声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比跳舞厅里的音响"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更有立体感，节奏感"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——还有四处的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鸟叫虫鸣蛙鼓伴奏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天上明月高挑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比跳舞厅里的灯光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更加明丽，柔媚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——还有无数"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闪烁的星星争相观赏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小夜风不停地吹着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比跳舞厅里的空调"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更加自然，凉爽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——还有周围"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"稻谷芳草野花飘香"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}